reviewText: ILSA-IS THE BLOFELD FOR NAZI GERMANY, SHE IS BOTH RUTHLESS AND CUNNING.SHE USES ELABORATE SCHEME OF TORTURE TO BREAK HER ENEMIES.SEX IS HER MOST DANGEROUS WEAPON TO FURTHER HER LUST FOR POWER.FRIENDS DIE TO BE WITH HER, AND THEY ALSO DIE TO EXCAPE HER LIFE OF DANGER.SHE DOESN'T MIND BETRAYING HER HEART TO GET AHEAD IN LIFE.FINALLY, ILSA-HAREM KEEPER OF THE OIL SHEIK IS NAILBITING FILM WITH A FIERY CLIMAX.THIS IS A 1970'S POPCORN MOVIE WITH LOTS OF ACTION,YOU CAN'T OVERLOOK THE PERFORMANCE OF DYANNE THORNE AS ILSA.DEADLIER THAN BOND,SEXIER THAN EMMANUELLLE.
